Mplus Print IRT Parameterization

Source: R/mplus_print.R
mplus.print.irt.parameterization.Rd

Show the IRT parameterization

Usage

mplus.print.irt.parameterization(file, invariance = 0)

Arguments

file

the quoted name of an existing H5 file

invariance

0 (not invariance model, default)

Value

A data frame containing the IRT parameterization results

Examples


ex5_5 <- system.file("extdata", "ex5_5.h5", package = "mplush5")
irt_results <- mplus.print.irt.parameterization(ex5_5)
irt_results
